    "description": "Tetromino X is a collection of games in the falling block action puzzle game genre. Each game has its own unique spin.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tetromino Stack</strong> is a test of balance and control where you must pick up and stack tetrominoes using gravity to your advantage without letting any fall.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0647ffa93666c8e882949a7e3635f34c.poster.avif?t=1732645360\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0647ffa93666c8e882949a7e3635f34c.webm?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0647ffa93666c8e882949a7e3635f34c.mp4?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tetromino Chill</strong> removes all stress from the genre, giving you an infinite plane where you can stack as many tetrominoes as you want without any pressure.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/9e62e7a991061b4290117f88b9b9c5ba.poster.avif?t=1732645360\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/9e62e7a991061b4290117f88b9b9c5ba.webm?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/9e62e7a991061b4290117f88b9b9c5ba.mp4?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Tetromino Match</strong> is a satisfying blend of the falling block and match 3 genres.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0efae04765047b76b55313bb423f730d.poster.avif?t=1732645360\" width=614 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0efae04765047b76b55313bb423f730d.webm?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/0efae04765047b76b55313bb423f730d.mp4?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Also includes several different block styles to choose from! (more to come)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/4ba1c2ec42a551d35ef962ae2287c11e.poster.avif?t=1732645360\" width=614 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/4ba1c2ec42a551d35ef962ae2287c11e.webm?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814120/extras/4ba1c2ec42a551d35ef962ae2287c11e.mp4?t=1732645360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
